About
ArcBest 
ArcBest is constantly evolving and leveraging the full 
force of our shipping and logistics solutions to meet our 
customers’ critical needs and keep the global supply chain 
moving. Founded in 1923 and now with 14,000 employees 
across more than 250 campuses and service centers, 
we’re a logistics powerhouse, fueled by the simple notion 
of finding a way to get the job done, no matter what.
